  m_Name: Crystallized
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  description: Your earthy towers have been mutated!
  traitIcon: {fileID: 8410776723451219211, guid: 3f639a2e1c4cb824ba1c789e14cf64ba, type: 3}
  breakpoints:
  - breakpointValue: 1
    breakpointDescription: The first shop each build phase is guaranteed to have
      an earthy tower.
  - breakpointValue: 3
    breakpointDescription: Destroyed crystallized towers shatter, dealing damage
      and leaving behind a crystal pylon.
  - breakpointValue: 5
    breakpointDescription: Bullets fired from crystallized towers will fracture,
      dealing damage and sometimes leaving a crystal pylon.
  - breakpointValue: 8
    breakpointDescription: Occasionally crystal pylons will fire lasers between each
      other pylon and crystal nexuses.
